Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
alignObject(25.10)                                          alignObject(25.10)

Name
       alignObject

Syntax
       alignObject

       [-help]

       -side {right | left | center | top | bottom | middle}

       [-referToFirst]

       [-mix]

       Aligns  objects  (instances, modules, or blockages) vertically or hori-
       zontally in the floorplan. Use this command after selecting two or more
       objects in the design display area.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes the type  and  default
              information  for  each alignObject parameter. For a detailed de-
              scription of the command and all of its parameters, use the  man
              command:

              man alignObject

       -mix   Considers all the selected objects together while aligning them.

              Data_type: bool, optional

       -referToFirst
              If  you  specify  this  option, the first selected object is the
              reference object.

              Data_type: bool, optional

       -side {right | left | center | top | bottom | middle}
              Specifies the vertical and horizontal alignment for the selected
              objects. Choose one of the following:

              * right: Specifies vertical right alignment.

              * left: Specifies vertical left alignment.

              * center: Specifies vertical center alignment.

              * top: Specifies horizontal top alignment.

              * bottom: Specifies horizontal bottom alignment.

              * middle: Specifies horizontal middle alignment.

              Data_type: string, required

Example
              *

                The following command aligns the selected objects (Block) ver-
                tically to the left:

                alignObject -side left

                Before:
                After:

              *

                The following command aligns the selected  objects  (Blockage-
                ModuleBlock) vertically to the left

                alignObject -side left -mix

                Before:                                                 After

              * The following command aligns the selected objects (Block) ver-
                tically to the left

                alignObject -side left -referToFirst

                Before
                After

